g.text: Estacin de Recepcin Migratoria (ERM)San Vicente (Darin) San Vincente, Panam
Migrants board a government bus costing $40 at San Vincente, Panam going to Chirqui in northern Panam.
The average migrant has spent $865 by the time they have made it past the Panam Canal.
Each arrow represents the accumulated cost a migrant has made. The average accumulated cost once migrants reach Chiriqui, Panam is $891 and they still have many kilometers left in their journey.
Bajo Chiquito is the first stopafter making the difficult walkthrough the Darin Jungle. Many migrants need food andwater.
